Package listener

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EDFFileFilter
    EDF file filters: five types of File filters (1) EDF filter: new EDFFileFilter({"edf"}, "EDF Files"); (2) EIA filter: new EDFFileFilter({"eia"}, "EIA Files"); (3) ESA filter: new EDFFileFilter({"esa"}, "ESA Files"); (4) EIA filter: new EDFFileFilter({"eia", "edf"}, "EIA and EDF Files"); (5) ESA filter: new EDFFileFilter({"esa", "edf"}, "ESA and EDF Files")
    SelectFilesListener
    This class is to act as the listener for the menu item "File to Select Files" usage: fileSelectFilesItem.addActionListener(frame, eiaTable, esaTable)
